

# Generalist Marketer

We are seeking a Generalist Marketer to assist Azuro in solidifying its position as a leader in decentralized betting technology by providing value in various areas of our presence: websites, PR, events, branding, and content.

### The ideal candidate will:

- Have a broad marketing background with strong experience and knowledge
- Either be familiar with crypto/web3 or have a strong desire and capacity to learn quickly
- Be comfortable taking ownership and getting things done
- Possess a lot of energy and drive to create and achieve in a fast-paced environment

### How to Apply

Send us a message explaining why you believe you are the right fit, and include information (CV/LinkedIn) about your relevant experience.
